sequenceDiagram
    participant Clerk as Accounting Clerk
    participant UI as Payment Modal
    participant InvoiceService as Invoice Service
    participant PaymentService as Payment Service
    participant JournalService as Journal Service
    participant DB as Database

    Clerk->>UI: Open payment modal for invoice #INV-123
    UI->>InvoiceService: getInvoiceDetails(INV-123)
    InvoiceService-->>UI: Invoice data (balance due, customer)
    UI->>Clerk: Display invoice balance

    Clerk->>UI: Enter amount, date, reference, payment method
    Clerk->>UI: Submit payment

    UI->>PaymentService: recordPayment(invoiceId, amount, date, ref, method)
    PaymentService->>DB: begin transaction
    PaymentService->>InvoiceService: applyPayment(invoiceId, amount)
    InvoiceService->>DB: update invoice balance
    InvoiceService-->>PaymentService: payment applied

    PaymentService->>JournalService: createJournalEntry(payment details)
    JournalService->>DB: insert journal entry (debit bank, credit accounts receivable)
    JournalService-->>PaymentService: journal entry created

    PaymentService->>DB: commit transaction
    PaymentService-->>UI: success (new payment record)

    UI->>Clerk: Show success message & updated invoice balance